                "title": "神里流·霜灭"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】此角色被切换为「出战角色」时，附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冰元素附魔</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/47826599/7359eeec791acae26196aa72a0621268_1289171544244615265.png",
