              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>造成2点<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/24/47826599/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2528330285932483395.png",
                "id": "talent46738",
                "key": "霜见雪关扉",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/24/47826599/1447ebe24c4e7bd955c4b795be517cd3_8149163626199186035.png",
                "title": "霜见雪关扉"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/24/47826599/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_513307435996783212.png",
                "id": "talent94341",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">冰元素附魔</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>所附属角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>。</p><p>（持续到回合结束）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/24/47826599/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_5861020943365701019.png",
